          <div class="panel panel-default panel-no-radius">
            <div class="panel-heading panel-heading-white">
              <h5 class="weather-date">01/02/2017</h5>
              <small class="weather-description">Sol com muitas nuvens durante o dia. Período de nublado, com chuva a qualquer hora.</small>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body panel-body-gray">
              <div class="row">
